code: import axios from"axios";export function loadPurchases(size,page,sort,order,search){return axios({method:"get",url:"/api/private/purchases",params:{size:size,page:page,sort:sort,order:order,search:search}}).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(){return false;});}export function createNewPurchase(newPurchase){return axios({method:"post",url:"/api/private/purchases",data:newPurchase}).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(error){debugger;return false;});}export function updatePurchase(purchaseToEdit){return axios({method:"post",url:"/api/private/purchases/update",data:purchaseToEdit}).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(){return false;});}export function deletePurchase(purchaseToDelete){return axios({method:"delete",url:"/api/private/purchases/"+purchaseToDelete.id}).then(function(){return true;}).catch(function(){return false;});}
